description.en: Deploys a device that reduces the reload time of allies within {ActRadius} by {ActEfficiency}.
Restores {ShieldHP} shield per second for {Duration}.
Deploys a sticky emitter, which reduces enemies' damage in area by {ActEfficiency} for {Duration}.
Plants a bomb within {Range}. After a short delay, explosion inflicts {Dmg} damage and knocks back enemies.
Deploys a {WallSize} wide barrier that stops enemies and absorbs up to {FieldHP} damage.
Creates a Camouflage Web with a radius of {DomeRad} for {Duration}, making allies inside it invisible to enemies outside. Cooldown {CD}.
Returns {Feedback} of incoming damage back at the enemy for {Duration}.
After a {BlinkSpeed} delay, teleport over {Dist} in a direction you're facing.
Fires a homing projectile that deals {Dmg} damage and blinds target for {Duration}.
Deploys a barrier with {DomeRad} radius that absorbs up to {DomeHP} damage from enemy attacks.
Generates a barrier that blocks projectiles and slowly travels forward for {ActDuration} seconds. All enemies passing through it receive {Dmg} per second. Cooldown: {CD}.
Refills up to {FuelMax} fuel at {RegenFuel} units per tick.
Deploys a turret that attacks the closest enemy for {Dmg} damage per shot over {ActDuration}.
Burns {Eff} fuel from the target and blocks its regeneration for {Duration}. Cooldown {CD}, {Consum} charges.
Fires a homing missile that deals {ArmorDmg} damage to all armor segments in the blast area or {HullDmg} to shields.

HumanDescription.SourceString: Fires homing misile at a highlited target, dealing  {HullDmg} damage to shield or {ArmorDmg} damage to armor for every robot component in the blast area.
HumanDescription.LocalizedString: Fires a homing missile that deals {ArmorDmg} damage to all armor segments in the blast area or {HullDmg} to shields.

description.en: After a {CastDuration} delay, grants unlimited ammo for {Duration}.

HumanDescription.SourceString: After a {CastDuration} preparation, weapons don't spend ammo for {Duration}. Charge needed: {ChargeDrain}.
HumanDescription.LocalizedString: After a {CastDuration} delay, grants unlimited ammo for {Duration}.

description.en: Refills {AmmoPerc} of ammo after a {CastDuration} delay.
Reduces all damage taken by {ActEfficiency} for {Duration}. Charge needed: {ChargeDrain}.
Fires a projectile that sticks to a surface or robot and emits {ActCount} pulses, pushing enemies at a distance of {ActRadius} in different directions. Cooldown {CD}. {Consum} charges.
Deploys an invisible minefield lasting {Duration}. Each mine slows enemies on impact and deals {Dmg} damage.
Repairs your most damaged module for {RegenSpeed}% of armor per second. Lasts {Duration}.
Repairs all modules for {RegenSpeed}% armor per tick. Lasts {Duration}.
Deals {Dmg} damage to enemies, and pushes them and you away from each other with {Force} force.
Deploys a {WallSize} wide wall that blocks line of sight for {Duration}.
Boosts you maximum speed by {SpeedBoost} for {Duration}.
Robot gains a speed boost and reveals all enemies in {ActRadius} range for {ActDuration}.
Locks onto the enemy for {ActDuration}, dealing up to {Dmg} damage per second. Damage scales with proximity.

HumanDescription.SourceString: Places a static impenetrable dome with {DomeRad} radius for {ActDuration}. The dome can't be damaged until its lifetime has expired. Charge needed: {ChargeDrain}.
HumanDescription.LocalizedString: Deploys a barrier with a {DomeRad} radius that protects against attacks from above. Last for {ActDuration}.

description.en: Deploys a barrier with a {DomeRad} radius that protects against attacks from above. Last for {ActDuration}.

Fires a device that attaches to solid surfaces. It then reveals enemies within {ActRadius} for {ActDuration} even if they are invisible. Cooldown: {CD}.
Fires a device that attaches to solid surfaces. It then reveals enemies within {ActRadius} for {ActDuration} even if they are invisible. Cooldown: {CD}.
Charge {Dist} forward, knocking enemies aside and dealing {Dmg} damage to all in your path. Cooldown: {CD}.
Deploys a fleet drones that intercept enemy projectiles within {ActRadius} every {SingulationRt}. Cooldown: {CD}.
Releases a static discharge that bounces off to nearby targets. It deals {Dmg} damage and prevents enemies from using gear for {ActDuration}. Cooldown: {CD}.
Marks an area for a devastating orbital strike that deals {Dmg} per tick to enemies within {ActRadius}. Cooldown: {CD}.
Replaces your weapon with swirling blades for {ActDuration}. They shred nearby enemies for {Dmg} damage per hit and restore your armor. Cooldown: {CD}.
Releases drones that deal {Dmg} damage per tick to enemies within {ActRadius}, while also lowering their accuracy and rate of fire. Cooldown: {CD}.
Activates a built-in electric weapon for {ActDuration}. It automatically picks a target near your crosshair, dealing {Dmg} damage per shot to a random module. Cooldown: {CD}.
Fires a volley of homing missiles, each dealing {ShieldDmg} to shields and {StructDmg} to armor. Cooldown: {CD}.
Creates a Camouflage Web with a radius of {DomeRad} for {Duration}, making allies inside it invisible to enemies outside. Cooldown {CD}.
Activates a built-in barrier and extra weapons that deal {Dmg} damage per shot for {ActDuration}.
Bombards an area, dealing {Dmg} damage per rocket to all modules within a {ActRadius} blast radius.
Mitigates {DmgResist} of incoming damage for {ActDuration}. Projectiles caught in the sphere refill your ammo.
After a short delay, unleashes an energy beam that deals {Dmg} per second for {ActDuration}. Your robot can't walk while it's active.
Repairs {RegenSpeed}% of armor per second. If any allies are within {ActRadius}, it repairs them as well and doubles the repair rate. Lasts 10 seconds.
Burns off {HPCostRat} of your current armor to boost weapon damage for 10 sec. While active, converts {Vamp} of damage inflicted into shield and armor.
Refills {AmmoPerc} of ammo after a {CastDuration} delay.
Prevents enemies from locking on to allies within {ActRadius} and splits all incoming damage between modules. Lasts {ActDuration}. Any robot affected cannot be destroyed.
Deploys a magnetic trap that lasts {ActDuration} and immobilizes enemies within {ActRadius} for a short time. Cooldown: {CD}.
Fires a projectile that deals {RocketDmg} blast damage on impact, then {Burning} fire damage over time.
Nearby allies deal {ActEfficiency} more damage for {ActDuration}. Effect increases whenever they score kills or destroy shields.

Infects an enemy robot with a virus that deals {Burning} damage per second for 6 seconds. If another enemy comes within {ActRadius} during the effect, the virus jumps to them. Can chain up to 8 times.
The robot teleports to a selected spot and casts a {ActEfficiency} damage reduction on itself and all allies nearby. The buff lasts for {ActDuration}
Allies within {ActRadius} take {DmgResist} less damage. Whenever they get hit, you regenerate armor.

Makes you invisible and projects a copy of your robot for {ActDuration}. The decoy has {ActEfficiency} more armor and shields, and all active effects including from gear modules are transferred to it.
Creates a wide area that speeds up allies for {ActDuration} and restores {RegenSpeed}% of armor per tick. Cooldown: {CD}.
Restores {ShieldRegen} shield per second for allies within {ActRadius} and half this value for Mesa itself. Also reduces damage output for enemies in range by 30%. Cooldown: {CD}.
Deals {ShieldDmg} shield damage in a straight line, revealing enemies for {ActDuration}.
Activate to mark a spot for {BeaconTime}. Activate again to warp back to that spot after a {TeleportSpeed} delay.
After a {FadeSpeed} second delay, you become invisible for {Duration}. Gear modules can be used while invisible, but firing weapons reveals the robot immediately. Cooldown: {CD}.
Allies in front of you take {DmgResist} less damage for {ActDuration}. You cannot be destroyed while any ally is affected by this.
Fires a barrage of missiles dead ahead, each dealing {Dmg} damage with a {ActRadius} blast radius.
A homing projectile deals {Dmg} damage on hit and then {Burning} per second to all modules. Recharges if target is destroyed while active.
Fires a freezing projectile that deals {Dmg} damage to enemies within a blast radius and immobilizes them for {FreezeDur}.
Generates a barrier that blocks projectiles and slowly travels forward for {ActDuration} seconds. All enemies passing through it receive {Dmg} per second. Cooldown: {CD}.
Fires homing missiles that force up to 3 enemies to reload, while also slowing their reloads by {JamRelSlow} for {JamDur}.
Deploys a drone that repairs allies within {ActRadius} for {ActDuration}.
Deploys a barrier with {DomeRad} radius that absorbs up to {DomeHP} damage from enemy attacks.
Deploys a bomb with a huge blast zone. Simple, effective, and devastating.
